
Installation:
=============

extract it where you want (<installation-folder>)
sudo ln -s <installation-folder>/lyrics-applet/bonobo/servers/LyricsApplet.server /usr/lib/bonobo/servers/LyricsApplet.server
sudo ln -s <installation-folder>/lyrics-applet/lyrics_applet.py /usr/lib/gnome-applets/lyrics-applet
sudo cp <installation-folder>/lyrics-applet/lyrics.png /usr/share/pixmaps/

(lyrics_applet.py should be already executable, if not: chmod +x <installation-folder>/lyrics-applet/lyrics_applet.py)

Debugging:
==========

cd /usr/lib/gnome-applets
python lyrics-applet -w

or

cd <installation-folder>/lyrics-applet/
python lyrics_applet.py -w
